Class IfcFeatureIgnorer

FeatureIgnorerExt
public class IfcFeatureIgnorer
extends Object
implements FeatureIgnorerExt

An extension for the FeatureIgnorerExt extension point that makes sure that some feature values are not taken into account during join point detection and model comparison.
